  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><span>On </span><span>May 16th</span><span> at 4:</span><span>14</span><span>&nbsp;PM PDT,</span><span> one of our clusters experienced an infrastructure issue that impacted our data ingestion process. </span><span>The issue was resolved on</span><span>&nbsp;May 17th at 9:</span><span>10 AM PDT.</span></p>\n\n<p><span>During this time frame,</span><span> approximately 40-50% of the events collected by customers in the Frankfurt region were not ingested into our database. </span><span>However, the impacted data is securely backed up</span><span> and we are currently working on restoring it.</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HYC9F54VN114G93E2M9CPVF0\"><span>Timeline</span></h2>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span>May 16, 4:14&nbsp;PM PDT</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">First incident of data ingestion disruption occurred</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span>May 17, 9:10 AM PDT</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">All data ingestion processes returned to normal and restoration efforts began</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><span>May 20, 5:42 PM PDT</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Data restoration efforts and root cause analysis ongoing</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span>We will provide further updates and a full incident report on this page as soon as the data restoration and root cause investigations are complete.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"23:1-23:119\"><span>We understand the importance of reliable data collection and sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. </span><span>We appreciate your patience and understanding as we resolve this issue.</span></p>"
      },
